Name: Baptists (band)

text: Baptists is a Canadian hardcore punk band from Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada, formed in 2010 by Andrew Drury, Danny Marshall, Shawn Hawryluk and Nick Yacyshyn.
Baptists have been categorized as metallic hardcore,[4][5] crust punk[4][6][5] and hardcore punk.[7][6][8][2]
